name: Saito
public_notice: Saito has recently expanded to Binance Smart Chain. For more info, read here.

description.en: Saito is a Web3 Foundation grant recipient that runs blockchain applications directly in your browser. The network pays ISPs instead of miners or stakers, allowing Web3 projects to self-fund infrastructure instead of passing costs to predatory monopolies like Infura.
